com.launchdarkly.sdk.internal.fdv2.payloads

Class PutObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.launchdarkly.sdk.internal.fdv2.payloads.PutObject

  • public final class PutObject
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the put-object event, which contains a payload object that should be accepted with upsert semantics. The object can be either a flag or a segment.
